ute with other users due to online transactions, you may not request this website through judicial or administrative means. (6) Taxes payable as a result of your use of the services provided by this website, as well as all hardware, software, services and other costs shall be judged and borne by you.</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\">(7) You shall comply with this Agreement as well as other terms of service and operating rules issued and updated from time to time by this website, and have the right to terminate the use of the services provided by this website at any time.</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\">3. Cost of Services</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\">(1) You agree to pay the required fees to the Website.</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\">(2) The Website reserves the right to set user service fees in accordance with appropriate regulations. The Website also has the right to set and adjust service fees and set specific service fees for your use of the Website\'s services. All changes to the fees will be announced in advance.</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\">(3) If you do not agree with any fee changes. You should stop using the service immediately. You will still be liable for any fees previously incurred.</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\">(4) Unless otherwise stated or agreed, the user agrees that this website has the right to automatically deduct the above service fees from the assets of the user\'s account without prior notice.</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\">4. Privacy Statement</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\">This Privacy Statement applies to all relevant services of this website, which respects and protects the personal privacy of all users of the platform services. In order to provide you with more accurate and personalized services, your personal information will be used and disclosed in accordance with this Privacy Policy, but the Website will treat such information with a high degree of caution. Unless otherwise specified in this Privacy Policy, the Website shall not disclose or provide such information to third parties without your prior permission. This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time. You are deemed to have agreed to this Privacy Policy in its entirety when you agree to this Site Service Agreement. This Privacy Policy is an integral part of the Service Agreement.</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\">Value Added Disclaimer</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\">Article 1</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\">1. Trading in digital assets carries a high level of risk and is not suitable for most people. You understand and appreciate that such trading may result in partial or total loss, and therefore you should determine the amount of such trading based on the level of loss you can afford to incur. You understand and appreciate the risks associated with the derivation of digital assets and are therefore advised to seek the assistance of a professional advisor if you are in any doubt. In addition, there will be unpredictable risks in addition to those described above. You should carefully consider and use your clear judgment in assessing your financial situation and the above risks and make any decision to buy or sel