ts, the website will, after checking the validity and authenticity of the judicial documents, assist in the provision of the corresponding user data or carry out the corresponding operations according to the requirements of the authorized institution determined by the platform. Therefore, the Website shall not be responsible for any loss caused to the user by the disclosure of the user\'s privacy or the failure of the account.</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\">Article 4</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\">Users using the services of this website should be aware before making transactions that digital assets are not supported by any government or central bank, that the price of digital assets fluctuates greatly, and that the risk of holding or using digital assets is high. Before making a trading decision, you should be rational and cautious about your financial situation to determine whether it is suitable for you.</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\">Article 5 If the users of this website violate the provisions of this statement and the relevant laws, this website, as a service provider, is obliged to improve the rules and services of this platform. However, this website does not violate the laws of Hong Kong related to the motives and facts, and does not bear any joint and several liability for the user\'s behavior.</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\">Article 6</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\">Any person who logs into this website in any way or uses the services of this website directly or indirectly shall be regarded as voluntarily bound by the statement of this website.</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\">Legal Statement</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\">Article 1</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\">The purpose of this website is to provide professional, safe and reliable digital asset trading and asset management services to as many digital asset enthusiasts and users around the world as possible without violating the relevant laws and regulations of the United States. However, if your country or region is a jurisdiction where digital asset trading is expressly prohibited by regulation or is included in the list of sanctioned countries, you shall be prohibited from using the services under this website.</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\">Article 2</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\">The platform is committed to creating a compliant, safe and reliable digital asset trading environment for users, and prohibits users from using this website to engage in any illegal trading activities or illegal behaviors such as money laundering, smuggling, commercial bribery, malicious market manipulation and so on. To this end, we make every effort to develop a strict anti-money laundering anti-terrorism program and take effective security risk control measures to maximize the protection of the legitimate rights and interests of users, so that the platform itself maintains a good brand reputation.</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\">Article 3</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\">When the competent authority generates corresponding investigation documents and requires the website to cooperate with the investigation of the designated users, or take measures such as seizing, freezing or transferring the user\'s account, the website will, after checking the validity and authenticity of the judicial documents, assist in providing the corresponding user\'s data or carry out the corresponding operation according to the requirements of the authorized institution determined by the platform. Therefore, it is not responsible for the losses caused to the users by the disclosure of the users\' privacy and the failure of their accounts.</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\">Article 4</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\">Users who use the services of this website should know before trading that digital assets are not supported by any government or central bank, the price of digital assets fluctuates greatly, and the risk of holding or using digital assets is high. Before making a trading decision, you should be rational and cautious about your financial situation to determine whether it is suitable for you.</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\">Article 5</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\">If a user of this website violates the provisions of this statement and violates the relevant laws, then this website, as a service provider, is obliged to improve the rules and services of this platform. However, this website does not violate the relevant laws, motives and facts, nor does it bear any joint and several liability for the user\'s behavior.</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\">Article 6</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\">Any person who logs into this website in any way or uses the services of this website directly or indirectly shall be regarded as voluntarily bound by the statement of this website.</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\">Article 7</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\">Please refer to the relevant laws and regulations of each country for issues not covered in this statement. If there is any conflict with the relevant laws and regulations of other countries, the relevant laws and regulations of other countries shall prevail.</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\">Our AML/CFT Programs</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\">We have designed an anti-money laundering and counter-terrorist financing program through a risk-based multi-level control system to reasonably prevent money laundering and terrorist financing.</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\">The first tier of the program consists of strict user identification procedures, including authentication of individual and corporate users.</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\">In addition to obtaining identification documents, we obtain information from non-natural person users about the beneficial owners/natural persons of their institutions, which meets international standards, such as the Financial Action Task Force (FATF) requirements.</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\">The second tier consists of risk-based system controls to ensure that additional customer due diligence is performed. For this purpose, we screen users (including beneficial owners) on the HKSARG Bulletin, the U.S. Office of Foreign Assets Control (OFAC) Sanctions List, the United Nations Security Council Sanctions List, and other sanction lists published by various agencies/lists of persons. We may also screen on other lists as appropriate to protect our reputation and clients.</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\">Tier 3 includes ongoing monitoring for suspicious activity. If we suspect, or have reason to suspect, suspicious transaction activity, we will file a suspicious transaction activity report with the local regulator, as appropriate. Often, suspicious transactions are inconsistent with legitimate business or personal day-to-day trading activities known to our customers.</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\">These are key components of our compliance program. However, the most important aspect of these multi-level risk control systems is our leadership team and staff, including AML/risk controllers, who conduct training, supervision and develop a good compliance culture.</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\">If you have any complaints, feedback or questions, please contact our Customer Service Department. When you contact us, please provide us with your name and email address and any other information we may need to identify you and what feedback, questions or complaints you have.</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"> Termination of this Agreement</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\">(1) The Site reserves the right to terminate all services on the Site pursuant to this Agreement, which shall terminate on the date of termination of all services on the Site.</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\">(2) Upon termination of this Agreement, you shall not have the right to require the Website to continue to provide any services or perform any other obligations, including without limitation, requiring the Website to retain or disclose any information in its original Website account, forward to you or to a third party any information not read or sent.</span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\">Translated with DeepL.com (free version)</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"></span></strong><br/></p>', 'en', NULL, 'N', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2024-03-27 12:07:30', 1178634832995377153);
